show.title: Thousand Years of Immortality
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/txe62k
show.description: Hero, after having cultivated in isolation for three thousand years, awakens to find that the tide of history has shifted, and the world has undergone tremendous changes. Right before his ascension, his final tribulation, the "Heart-Tempering in the Mundane World," begins to unfold in the modern city. He dressed in ragged clothes and with vacant eyes, wanders the streets, marveling at the new technological world. He happens upon the head of the Harold family, who is training with his bodyguards during their morning exercises. Then he settles down in the city, navigating the urban conflicts with a path of extraordinary ability.
